member.returns:
A byte greater than or equal to minValue and less than maxValue;
            that is, the range of return values includes minValue but not maxValue. If minValue
            equals maxValue, minValue is returned

A 16-bit signed short greater than or equal to minValue and less than maxValue;
            that is, the range of return values includes minValue but not maxValue. If minValue
            equals maxValue, minValue is returned

A 32-bit signed integer greater than or equal to minValue and less than maxValue;
            that is, the range of return values includes minValue but not maxValue. If minValue
            equals maxValue, minValue is returned

A 64-bit signed long greater than or equal to minValue and less than maxValue;
            that is, the range of return values includes minValue but not maxValue. If minValue
            equals maxValue, minValue is returned
